1.2
log
@Ignore MCFG tables with an empty bus range.  Makes stu@@'s amd64 machine
boot again.
@
text
@/* $OpenBSD: acpimcfg.c,v 1.1 2011/01/04 21:17:49 kettenis Exp $ */
/*
